data.description:
This beautiful home was newly built in 2021 and features 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. As you step through front door you are welcomed with beautiful, upgraded luxury vinyl flooring and 9ft ceilings, which is throughout the home. The layout of this home is perfect with two bedrooms and full bathroom on one side of hallway and third bedroom and bathroom on other side of hallway. The great room is very spacious with vaulted ceilings, opening up to the gourmet kitchen with island, gorgeous granite countertops, white shaker cabinets and stainless-steel appliances. Master bedroom is spacious with double sinks and walk in closet! The home features recessed lighting throughout, as well as smart home technology. This 16ft side yard also has the potential for RV parking!! Home features Solar as well!! This community is nested below the mountain ranges of Hemet, in the amazing new community of McSweeny Farms. Amenities including huge pool, full gym, Billiard room, playground, basketball courts, baseball field, playground, trails and picnic areas. Feel like you are in the country, but still close to local shopping, recreation and the 215 and 79 highways. Don't miss this beautiful home that can be yours to move in now!!

Pets accepted upon approval.
